NO, SAKAI, YOU'RE HUMAN.

15
00:02:39,791 --> 00:02:42,625
- EVEN AFTER SHE
FOUND OUT WHAT I WAS,

16
00:02:42,708 --> 00:02:45,500
YOSHIDA REVEALED HER
TRUE FEELINGS FOR ME.

17
00:02:45,583 --> 00:02:47,708
AND THEN, THERE WAS SHANA.

18
00:02:49,708 --> 00:02:50,666
- ( gasps )

19
00:02:54,333 --> 00:02:56,458
- WHAT SEEMS TO BE
BOTHERING YOU?

20
00:02:56,541 --> 00:02:57,666
- WIRHELMINA.

21
00:03:34,708 --> 00:03:36,375
- IT DOESN'T REALLY LOOK
LIKE YOU'VE BEEN LIVING

22
00:03:36,458 --> 00:03:37,708
IN THIS APARTMENT.

23
00:03:37,791 --> 00:03:40,458
- YEAH, YOU'RE RIGHT.

24
00:03:40,541 --> 00:03:41,666
- Tiamat: CLEAN-UP REQUIRED.

25
